preference.name: CATIA_check_catalog_staging_conflict_on_save
preference.preference_description: Indicates whether to display an error message, warning message or no message when staging conflicts occur while saving a catalog and its referenced documents. Possible values : NONE = Do not display a message and erase all documents in the staging area when staging conflicts occur while saving a catalog and its referenced documents. ERROR = Display an error message and stop the save process when staging conflicts occur while saving a catalog and its referenced documents. WARNING = Display a warning message when staging conflicts occur while saving a catalog and its referenced documents. Allows users to continue and erase the documents or cancel the save process.
